description: SUNDAY OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED. OFFER ACCEPTED. Calling all investors! This spacious, detached three-family gem in the heart of South Boston’s City Point is a solid investment. With three 2+ bedroom units and over 3,800 sq ft of living space, this property offers plenty of flexibility (City of Boston records indicate 3 bedrooms in each unit, but it's 2+ in each--see floor plans). The owner-occupied second-floor unit features some thoughtful updates, and each unit boasts large private decks overlooking a great backyard. You can’t beat the location—just two blocks from the beach, tucked between L & M Streets, and a short stroll to Broadway with all of Southie’s best dining and shopping. Plus, with easy access to the Seaport and downtown, this area is still seeing incredible growth with lots of new development. 1st & 2nd floors are vacant.
